verses.text_plain: Now Jephthah the Gileadite was a mighty man of valour, and he was the son of an harlot: and Gilead begat Jephthah.
verses.verse_html:
1Now Jephthah the Gileadite was a mighty man of valour, and he was the son of an harlot: and Gilead begat Jephthah. ▼
▼ Jephthah: Gr. Jephthae
 , ▼
▼ an harlot: Heb. a woman an harlot
